OL,5, Buy now, pay later firm Klarna is      
OL,6, extending its services, including      
OL,7, offering the choice of paying for items
OL,8, in full, immediately.                  
OL,10,FIt said the "pay now" option and other 
OL,11,Fchanges it was making would give       
OL,12,Fcustomers more clarity and control.    
OL,14,FBuy now, pay later firms such as Klarna
OL,15,Fhave seen business boom over the last  
OL,16,Ffew years.                             
OL,18,FHowever, charities warn they can make  
OL,19,Fit too easy to fall into debt and the  
OL,20,Fsector is facing tougher regulation.   
